        public Molecule[] getProducts(String reactants,
                              int aRxnId)
                       throws SynthError
        Gets the products from a group of reactants subject to particular reaction conditions. Called from public/synthTest.jsp.
        Parameters:
        reactants - MRV of reactants
        aRxnId - ID number of reaction conditions
        Returns:
        array of molecules that were calculated to be products
        Throws:
        SynthError - if products could not be calculated

                              String reactionDef,
                              boolean reverse)
                       throws SynthError
        Gets the products from a group of reactants subject to particular reaction conditions. Called from public/pasteSynth.jsp.
        Parameters:
        reactants - MRV of reactants
        reactionDef - a reaction definition in MRV format
        reverse - whether to run the reaction in reverse (calculate the starting materials from the products)
        Returns:
